{"tid":677073,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"戒酒Post","createTime":"2018-05-25T01:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T12:32:48.000Z","uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6f886a52ec766c71164464962aacd0ad9850b0f4","tid":677073,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T01:32:49.000Z","msg":"我大量飲酒都差不多七、八年<br />\n呢七八年嚟，健康差咗好多，個人無咁醒目<br />\n仲有肥咗、樣衰咗好多<br />\n工作表現同人際關係都唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得唔可以再係咁落去<br />\n上來一嚟立此為證<br />\n二嚟睇下有無巴打一齊互相支持<br />\n尋晚飲咗半支紅酒，因為係屋企最後一支存貨，飲剩半支倒咗，以示決心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後只會在特殊場合飲(例如去飲、旅行tasting)，但都會打上來記錄返。<br />\n直至覺得自己可以隨心所欲控制為止<br />\n大家嗰日無飲的話，夜晚一齊上來report，畀個like大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n彼此支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3c455733fd053150f367db32e69d7ba76b9f3e","tid":677073,"uid":88190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T06:39:11.000Z","msg":"Halo Bro<br />\n你好似好有決心...<br />\n唔知你近排情況點呢?"},{"pid":"3daf5b2e432f1677b7ab2fb140c4e7a89f1654c7","tid":677073,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:16:42.000Z","msg":"你點解唔早啲回覆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我隔咗八日今日剛剛破戒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你早啲覆我我今日一定頂到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a795ea70304bef1e22e2c908019bdde2dccc73","tid":677073,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:18:08.000Z","msg":"OK<br />\n再嚟過<br />\nDay 0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0953f75a4158a28fd2ded6a596362dabd6d6e4","tid":677073,"uid":88190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89a795ea70304bef1e22e2c908019bdde2dccc73","tid":677073,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:18:08.000Z","msg":"OK<br />\n再嚟過<br />\nDay 0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T12:41:46.000Z","msg":"咁你依個星期忍唔忍到戒酒呀?"},{"pid":"b736a06a525135b142b89959a8f70f968fb59e23","tid":677073,"uid":36533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:48:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edbcfd1f75b2c439fc749165b7d5c1a1c3cbee5f","tid":677073,"uid":179712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:08:06.000Z","msg":"連續砍左5日<br />\n工都無返<br />\n真係要戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e802ace36318a43aa8b1f671f7393d772d4da2e","tid":677073,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:32:48.000Z","msg":"飲咗二十幾年<br />\n<br />\n戒咗幾次<br />\n<br />\n支持巴打， 其實追酒飲先係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}